tion\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 727}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800m.\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is difficult to refer to him as a rival when he is never there,\\\" Ingebrigtsen prodded.\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 832, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a rival\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 785}, {\"ngram\": \"Ingebrigtsen\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He is known as the Brit who never competes.\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 877, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Brit\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 857}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I try to enter as many races as I can and I want to be here to entertain.\\\"\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 952, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"as many races\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 906}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This wasn't the end of the fighting talk though.\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 1002, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 973}, {\"ngram\": \"the fighting talk\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When Kerr set the indoor two-mile world record at the Millrose Games back in February, Ingebrigtsen stated: \\\"I would have beaten him in that race, blindfolded.\\\"\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1012}, {\"ngram\": \"the indoor two-mile world record\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1049}, {\"ngram\": \"the Millrose Games\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1071}, {\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1088}, {\"ngram\": \"Ingebrigtsen\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1102}, {\"ngram\": \"that race\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1148}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since then, attention has been focused on their showdown in Paris.\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1224, \"end\": 1229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.9176486074121884e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"ty